channel.title: Model of a gun
channel.description:
i was looking around the internet looking for ideas when i came across a gun. it was one of those old style ones so i decided to make a model of it. I converted everything all you need to do is drag to the model folder and add the ints.
if you can't get the ints part maybe you don't deserve this.
good luck if your going to use it i made this for moparscape.
here is a pic
[IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2por3g0.jpg[/img] sry the picture came out crapy is cause i used print screen and the gun was really small so i inlarged it made the gun look retarded you gotta download to see the real peice of work.
10451 is the weild model 10452 is the drop model
now for the link
[url=http://uppit.com/v/2PN1SYBN]http://uppit.com/v/2PN1SYBN[/url]
